    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Issue 2 - Stuck in Bootloader"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Information"
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "headers": [
        "Found in Project",
        "ECARX FX11",
        "RTC Ticket",
        "Story 1530119"
      ],
      "rows": []
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Analysis"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "CAN/LIN routing function is enabled in bootloader. And the DET is still enabled in bootloader."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "There is a chance to enter to Det_EndlessLoop due to errors in the network."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Solution"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Disable DET functionality in bootloader"
    },
